Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.78,0:00:08.32,Normal,NarratingM,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's something in this world that no one has ever seen.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.25,0:00:21.49,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,It's a stinkin' lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.46,0:00:25.88,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,These are just...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.72,0:00:32.54,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,What is this? It's friggin' molding!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.93,0:00:34.92,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,And I just cleaned the mold the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.04,0:00:37.98,Normal,NarratingM,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's something kind and very sweet.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.80,0:00:38.62,Backgroud,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Rags, I need a rag...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.11,0:00:43.82,Normal,NarratingM,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If it was something that was visible, people would probably want it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.45,0:00:51.92,Normal,NarratingF,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's why the world hid it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.37,0:00:55.05,Normal,NarratingF,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So that it wouldn't be so easy to attain.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.00,0:00:58.69,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,Darn, it won't come off.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.20,0:01:02.93,Normal,NarratingM,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}However, it will surely be attained by someone, someday.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.90,0:01:02.85,Backgroud,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}But if I use this, maybe then...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.31,0:01:08.69,Normal,NarratingF,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The single person that's supposed to attain it will be the one to find it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.64,0:01:17.37,Normal,NarratingFM,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's just how it is.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.62,0:01:36.02,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,Eco, eco, eco, ecology~{\fnArial}♪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.80,0:01:42.23,Notes,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\be1}{\an8\u1}TL Note:{\u0} Inko (鸚哥/いんこ) literally translates to "parakeet."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.80,0:01:42.23,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,Inko-chan, are you still sleeping?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.72,0:01:44.72,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,It's morning already...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.86,0:01:48.31,Normal,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Meow~ I gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.70,0:01:57.35,Normal,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuu-chan, you're so cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.35,0:01:59.98,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,I told you last night, I have school starting today.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.98,0:02:02.80,Normal,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, the entrance ceremony, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.80,0:02:04.57,Normal,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations on passing your grade.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.57,0:02:07.68,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,Is that the kind of attitude you should have towards your son whose going into a new school year?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.68,0:02:11.56,Normal,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, this room is dark. Could you open the curtains?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.87,0:02:12.62,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,They're open.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.29,0:02:13.60,Normal,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.86,0:02:19.15,Normal,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Ah—That's a huge apartment, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.14,0:02:21.66,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what kind of person lives there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.79,0:02:23.94,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since THIS was built, we've lost the grace of the sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.56,0:02:26.91,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,So the laundry dries poorly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.91,0:02:29.22,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,Every single day there's mold, mold, mold—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.45,0:02:33.60,Normal,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Those piercing eyes! Ryuu-chan, you look more like your papa.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.60,0:02:34.70,Normal,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,600)}...more like your papa.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.70,0:02:35.74,Normal,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,800)}...more like your papa.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.74,0:02:36.85,Normal,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,1000)}...more like your papa.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.33,0:02:38.70,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,Don't put me in the same boat as that—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.70,0:02:40.86,Normal,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my, so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.86,0:02:43.07,Normal,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Now you look even more like your papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.52,0:02:48.43,Normal,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Ryuu-chan, you're leaving already?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.56,0:02:50.05,Normal,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,What about my breakfast?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.95,0:02:51.99,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,It's in the usual place.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.31,0:02:54.17,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,That was...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.24,0:03:00.59,Normal,,0000,0000,0000,,That was the one thing I didn't want her to tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.08,0:03:09.44,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to these piercing eyes that you compliment me about— I...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.44,0:03:10.15,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.31,0:03:11.48,Normal,Kid1,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.66,0:03:13.06,Normal,Kid2,0000,0000,0000,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.50,0:03:14.07,Normal,Kid1,0000,0000,0000,,Woah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.81,0:03:15.22,Normal,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.39,0:03:15.51,Normal,Kid2,0000,0000,0000,,Ta-{\alpha&FF&}Ta-Ta-Ta-Takasu! Why did you do that man?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.51,0:03:15.67,Normal,Kid2,0000,0000,0000,,Ta-Ta-{\alpha&FF&}Ta-Ta-Takasu! Why did you do that man?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.67,0:03:15.77,Normal,Kid2,0000,0000,0000,,Ta-Ta-Ta-{\alpha&FF&}Ta-Takasu! Why did you do that man?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.77,0:03:16.01,Normal,Kid2,0000,0000,0000,,Ta-Ta-Ta-Ta-{\alpha&FF&}Takasu! Why did you do that man?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.01,0:03:17.03,Normal,Kid2,0000,0000,0000,,Ta-Ta-Ta-Ta-Takasu! {\alpha&FF&}Why did you do that man?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.03,0:03:18.18,Normal,Kid2,0000,0000,0000,,Ta-Ta-Ta-Ta-Takasu! Why did you do that man?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.93,0:03:19.65,Echo,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? What? Wh—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.18,0:03:19.50,Normal,Kid1,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that I meant to!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.06,0:03:21.58,Normal,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Please let us off the hook on this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.85,0:03:22.13,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.31,0:03:23.92,Normal,Kid2,0000,0000,0000,,This is all we have right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.92,0:03:24.78,Normal,Kid1,0000,0000,0000,,It's the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.78,0:03:26.37,Normal,Kid1,0000,0000,0000,,See, we're not making any jingling sounds, are we?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.37,0:03:26.98,Echo,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.98,0:03:29.16,Normal,Both,0000,0000,0000,,PLEASE FORGIVE US!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.09,0:03:29.83,Backgroud,Girl1,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}He's so scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.83,0:03:31.06,Backgroud,Girl2,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Those are a killer's eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.31,0:03:32.08,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.81,0:03:42.44,Normal,Old,0000,0000,0000,,Again? Sheesh, you pick up a lot of wallets, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.74,0:03:43.33,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.33,0:03:45.09,Normal,Girl1,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I hope we get in the same class again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.09,0:03:45.35,Normal,Girl2,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.36,0:03:50.24,Normal,Girl1,0000,0000,0000,,There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.24,0:03:52.03,Normal,Girl2,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! We're in the same class again!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.09,0:03:56.75,Backgroud,Girl1,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I'm scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.01,0:03:58.36,Backgroud,Guy1,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}That's a killer's eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.86,0:03:59.67,Backgroud,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}He's going to kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.95,0:04:00.42,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,Crap, this again?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.42,0:04:00.66,Normal,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.63,0:04:04.86,Normal,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,I guess we're in the same class this year too, Takasu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.58,0:04:06.51,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,Kitamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.09,0:04:10.57,Announce,Announcer,0000,0000,0000,,And this concludes this year's entrance ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.02,0:04:14.03,Announce,Announcer,0000,0000,0000,,Go to your respective classrooms and prepare for homeroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.03,0:04:19.79,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,A new class. I have to start by clearing up everyone's misconceptions again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.07,0:04:20.97,Normal,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,It's alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.13,0:04:23.62,Normal,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,At least it's not everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.26,0:04:25.54,Normal,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,I understand you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.82,0:04:29.47,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, thanks man.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.82,0:04:33.25,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,He's right; there are people who understand, like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.67,0:04:35.40,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, in this class is—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.53,0:04:36.75,Normal,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Heya, Kitamura-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.37,0:04:40.16,Normal,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,We're in the same class this year, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.26,0:04:41.43,Normal,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if it isn't Kushieda.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.66,0:04:42.72,Normal,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,So you're in Class C too?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.89,0:04:46.20,Normal,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu-kun, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.29,0:04:47.68,Normal,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.82,0:04:50.59,Normal,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,We've always passed by each other around Kitamura-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.33,0:04:54.87,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kushieda Minori...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.94,0:04:58.36,Normal,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, you remember my whole name?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.73,0:04:59.95,Normal,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.39,0:05:08.30,Normal,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, well then. Let's enjoy our youth together, eloquently and cheerfully!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.70,0:05:09.14,Normal,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.47,0:05:10.75,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.02,0:05:13.28,Normal,Guy1,0000,0000,0000,,And then it—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.28,0:05:16.10,Normal,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Takasu?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.30,0:05:19.29,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing, I just need to use the restroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.29,0:05:20.94,Normal,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so? I'll just go on ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.94,0:05:29.85,Normal,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,Is there going to be a major battle?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.52,0:05:34.35,Normal,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu Ryuuji and Aisaka Taiga! The two most powerful cards have suddenly made their moves!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.45,0:05:35.94,Normal,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,Is this going to be the deciding battle!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.79,0:05:39.60,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,What the?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.22,0:05:43.17,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,She sure has a small body. She's like a doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.72,0:05:45.23,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,But, something—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.45,0:05:49.23,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,But, something feels strangely overbearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.51,0:05:51.79,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,It's like she might just snatch me up and eat me if I let my guard down.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.05,0:05:53.17,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,Um... this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.17,0:05:54.65,Normal,Girl1,0000,0000,0000,,You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.65,0:05:56.75,Normal,Girl1,0000,0000,0000,,Delinquent Takasu-kun and the Palmtop Tiger are—!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.75,0:05:57.26,Normal,Girl1,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.05,0:06:00.67,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,Palmtop... Tiger...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.00,0:06:02.76,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.35,0:06:04.06,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,Palmtop Tai—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.74,0:06:08.37,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,1000)}What the hell... it matches perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.15,0:06:14.58,Normal,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, that will be all for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.95,0:06:18.64,Normal,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,If you haven't submitted your career choice form, come to the teacher's office later.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.62,0:06:20.91,Normal,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay, Takasu-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.06,0:06:22.06,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.97,0:06:27.53,Normal,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Are you alright, Taiga?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.70,0:06:29.16,Normal,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,You were late, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.59,0:06:31.75,Normal,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I went to see the doctor for nasal allergies.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.06,0:06:34.01,Normal,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Something about house dust or whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.01,0:06:35.26,Normal,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, a modern day allergy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.64,0:06:36.94,Normal,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,That must be quite a bother.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.99,0:06:43.26,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,Palmtop Tiger. So she's friends with Kushieda Minori.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.31,0:06:45.89,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh, the one that's bothered is over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.38,0:06:47.23,Normal,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,Are you alright man?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.13,0:06:50.02,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,Hey. Yeah, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.67,0:06:51.33,Normal,Glassse,0000,0000,0000,,But yeah—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.71,0:06:52.98,Normal,Girl1,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't that amazing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.98,0:06:54.50,Normal,Girl1,0000,0000,0000,,I mean Aisaka-san and Takasu-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.50,0:06:56.61,Normal,Boy1,0000,0000,0000,,Palmtop Tiger is as strong as I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.61,0:06:59.53,Normal,Boy2,0000,0000,0000,,Plus Takasu-kun is just scary looking, he isn't an actual delinquent.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.53,0:07:00.28,Normal,Girl2,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.41,0:07:02.25,Normal,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like their misconception will be gone quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.25,0:07:02.99,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.94,0:07:04.74,Normal,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.60,0:07:06.52,Normal,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.90,0:07:08.94,Normal,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,N-Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.58,0:07:14.78,Normal,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,T-Takasu-kun, is it possible that you've lost the path that you want to chose?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.15,0:07:15.47,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.58,0:07:20.77,Normal,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,B-B-But you see, you have to submit a career form. Everyone other than you already has...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.23,0:07:22.98,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm sorry, I just—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.54,0:07:24.52,Normal,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.52,0:07:27.56,Normal,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,I bet you don't want some single person, who's wasting time on her path, to be preaching to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.56,0:07:29.08,Normal,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for being so vain!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.84,0:07:33.50,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm late.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.39,0:07:36.00,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,My time saving is going to be ove—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.43,0:07:56.73,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,A-Are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.80,0:08:01.42,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,My bag... my bag...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.19,0:08:04.93,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'll just leave her alone for now...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.16,0:08:07.75,Normal,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Y-{\alpha&FF&}You!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.75,0:08:08.21,Normal,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.21,0:08:08.53,Normal,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Wha-{\alpha&FF&}What-What are-Wha-What are you--?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.53,0:08:08.90,Normal,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Wha-What-{\alpha&FF&}What are-Wha-What are you--?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.90,0:08:09.33,Normal,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Wha-What-What are-{\alpha&FF&}Wha-What are you--?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.33,0:08:09.67,Normal,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Wha-What-What are-Wha-{\alpha&FF&}What are you--?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.67,0:08:10.19,Normal,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Wha-What-What are-Wha-What are you--?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.23,0:08:10.19,Echo,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.18,0:08:12.19,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,Look, I'm just here to grab my bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.95,0:08:14.48,Normal,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Your bag?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.48,0:08:16.23,Normal,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Your seat is the one next to—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.81,0:08:19.26,Normal,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be that the let—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.26,0:08:19.96,Normal,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,L-{\alpha&FF&}L-L-L-Le-Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.96,0:08:20.36,Normal,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,L-L-{\alpha&FF&}L-L-Le-Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.36,0:08:20.50,Normal,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,L-L-L-{\alpha&FF&}L-Le-Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.50,0:08:20.81,Normal,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,L-L-L-L-{\alpha&FF&}Le-Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.81,0:08:21.27,Normal,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,L-L-L-L-Le—{\alpha&FF&}Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.27,0:08:22.56,Normal,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,LET {\alpha&FF&}GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.56,0:08:23.54,Normal,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,LET GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.10,0:08:29.99,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you want my bag?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.73,0:08:34.20,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Give it a rest alread—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.05,0:08:42.81,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,You know—!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.97,0:08:46.45,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,A-Aisaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.40,0:08:53.41,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.36,0:08:56.79,Normal,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Dumbass!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.24,0:09:01.43,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,This is so messed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.18,0:09:06.48,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,So messed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.38,0:09:22.70,Echo,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,0)}Your papa's in heaven, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.12,0:09:24.92,Echo,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,He was such a cool person!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.92,0:09:28.69,Echo,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,He always had a magazine in front of his chest in case he were to get stabbed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.10,0:09:30.31,Echo,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,1000)}It gives me tingles!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.90,0:09:32.81,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,Just because I look like you,...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.49,0:09:36.29,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm having alot of trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.07,0:09:41.55,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,If I didn't have a face like this... Everyone wouldn't be afraid of me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.08,0:09:44.20,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,Palmtop Tiger wouldn't pick a fight with me either.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.35,0:09:47.33,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,I would be able to have more confidence in myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.79,0:09:49.50,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,Then I could—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.06,0:09:53.07,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,The career choice form...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.28,0:09:56.66,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.54,0:10:00.41,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,To Kitamura Yuusaku-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.62,0:10:04.07,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,Aisaka... Taiga.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.12,0:10:07.08,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.96,0:10:12.59,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,"You put this in the wrong one, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.96,0:10:16.76,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't look at its contents at all so I have no clue what's in there but—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.76,0:10:18.44,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just go ahead and return it to you!"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.74,0:10:22.14,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,Oh crap! I have to stick it back on!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.40,0:10:31.03,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be that she's... a major klutz?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.78,0:10:35.33,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.86,0:10:53.95,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Yasuko... isn't home yet, is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.24,0:10:57.22,Normal,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! I'm gonna chug it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.04,0:10:58.70,Backgroud,Guys,0000,0000,0000,,Go, go! Mirano-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.18,0:11:03.15,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,Heeey...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.16,0:11:08.05,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,The window's—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.05,0:11:11.99,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,THAT {\alpha&FF&}HURTS!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.99,0:11:13.02,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,THAT HURTS!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.54,0:11:21.14,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,W-What in the--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.56,0:11:26.73,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? This size...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.95,0:11:27.83,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,Somewhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.83,0:11:43.25,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,AISAKA!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.31,0:11:47.84,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,USE A TISSUE!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.92,0:11:52.63,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,What...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.00,0:11:58.54,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.14,0:11:59.67,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,...are...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.31,0:12:00.86,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,...you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.27,0:12:01.88,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,...do...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.29,0:12:03.21,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,...ing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.27,0:12:05.34,Normal,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.34,0:12:07.68,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Forget it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.07,0:12:09.68,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,Ohhh, that let—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.84,0:12:11.24,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,-ter...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.21,0:12:17.19,Normal,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Now that it's been found out, I can live no longer... I must die!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.36,0:12:19.13,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,Then why are you trying to friggin' kill me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.25,0:12:22.04,Normal,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to die, so I have to kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.61,0:12:25.51,Normal,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise, completely forget about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.81,0:12:26.92,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,That's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.14,0:12:29.11,Normal,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.68,0:12:35.12,Normal,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,It may be impossible to kill you with one strike to the brain, but it should at least wipe that memory of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.34,0:12:37.80,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,Don't wipe it! Alright, just listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.80,0:12:38.54,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,That letter—!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.29,0:12:39.04,Echo,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.70,0:12:41.98,Normal,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,SHUT UP, SHUT UP!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.30,0:12:44.37,Normal,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,You saw it, didn't you?! You read it, didn't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.81,0:12:45.98,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'm saying I—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.54,0:12:47.87,Normal,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to listen to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.87,0:12:52.18,Normal,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,That's why, about that lo-lo-love-love letter...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.57,0:12:53.97,Normal,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,FORGET EVERYTHING!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.85,0:12:56.39,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,IT WAS EMPTY!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.68,0:13:03.05,Normal,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Em—pty?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.86,0:13:06.91,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,Right, so I don't know anything about the contents.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.50,0:13:10.31,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,You were lucky that Kitamura didn't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.69,0:13:12.66,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't have to go through a blunder.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.02,0:13:15.73,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.00,0:13:26.97,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,How starved are you anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.98,0:13:33.10,Normal,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I got bored with the convenience store.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.10,0:13:34.01,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,The convenience store?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.49,0:13:36.04,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Don't your parents make your mea—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.06,0:13:39.69,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose everyone has their own household issues.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.37,0:13:40.67,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.65,0:13:50.54,Normal,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,If you would have just handed the bag quietly back then, this wouldn't have happened in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.12,0:13:52.97,Normal,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,How are you going to take responsibility for this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.13,0:13:54.28,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,There's still some on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.98,0:14:02.49,Normal,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Hearing that from a guy whose sole purpose in life was to put garlic flavoring into this fried rice...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.48,0:14:04.54,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,Now look here—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.37,0:14:15.33,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with a love letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.62,0:14:18.02,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing shameful about it at all, you hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.31,0:14:18.91,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,Just wait there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.54,0:14:22.96,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,Take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.04,0:14:25.88,Normal,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.71,0:14:30.28,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know what that is?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.42,0:14:31.50,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,I bet you don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.10,0:14:37.73,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,That's a list of songs I would play if I were to put on a concert for the girl I like. {That's a list that I created based on the kind of concert that I would make for the girl that I like.}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.55,0:14:40.84,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,That was something I just happened to make for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.26,0:14:43.35,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,Mini-discs that I'd play while driving with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.35,0:14:44.32,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, I don't even have a driver's license.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.64,0:14:46.61,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,I've planned something for all seasons of the year. {was "created"}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.25,0:14:49.09,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,How's it? Creepy, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.48,0:14:52.73,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't have the courage to ask them out, all you can do is fantasize like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.52,0:14:57.08,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,It certainly is pitiful... but I still don't think it's shameful!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.38,0:14:58.97,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,You need to have some confidence in yourself, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.65,0:15:03.02,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't stick with fantasizing and actually moved into action!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.79,0:15:06.98,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,Just look to the future, keep a positive attitude, and do it and cheerfully!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.08,0:15:09.05,Normal,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,"I offer this to Miss Kushieda Minori."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.24,0:15:11.51,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,Right, just like Kushieda Minori.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.39,0:15:14.78,Normal,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,You like Minori?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.60,0:15:16.78,Normal,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,How offensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.41,0:15:19.05,Normal,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,You should know your place.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.81,0:15:22.20,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! You're one to talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.42,0:15:24.41,Normal,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with you?! You just told me you'd forget—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.43,0:15:30.22,Normal,Inko,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Cold, it's cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.91,0:15:32.98,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry Inko-chan. Did we wake you up?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.67,0:15:35.87,Normal,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you showing me that disgusting thing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.87,0:15:38.28,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,What did you just say about one of my precious family members?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.28,0:15:40.09,Normal,Inko,0000,0000,0000,,I— I—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.09,0:15:43.11,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, Inko-chan! Introduce yourself to the guest!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.34,0:15:45.27,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,Today will be the day when you finally say your name!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.68,0:15:46.66,Normal,Inko,0000,0000,0000,,I~
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.66,0:15:48.66,Normal,Inko,0000,0000,0000,,In~
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.66,0:15:49.23,Normal,Inko,0000,0000,0000,,In*po*
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.83,0:15:58.24,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,Inko-chan isn't on top shape today, I swear.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.33,0:16:01.12,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,Crap, it's already this late!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.06,0:16:05.07,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, we're in the same situation!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.07,0:16:06.36,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,I won't tell anyone about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.36,0:16:07.25,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.58,0:16:07.85,Normal,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.15,0:16:11.59,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?! Hold on, you even ate here, just go home already!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.75,0:16:13.02,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,No, please leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.20,0:16:15.20,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,My mother who's ill, in a matter of speaking, is about to come home.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.31,0:16:16.92,Normal,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,N{\alpha&FF&}O WAY! {+}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.92,0:16:17.56,Normal,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,NO {\alpha&FF&}WAY! {+}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.56,0:16:17.92,Normal,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,NO WAY!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.96,0:16:20.62,Normal,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I can't trust you anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.80,0:16:26.70,Normal,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Plus... Is a love letter alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.30,0:16:28.87,Normal,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Is it something you'd do now-a-days?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.34,0:16:31.15,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,You can't suddenly get so fidgety at a time like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.87,0:16:34.03,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,You can consult me with any love problems, but it's really late right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.60,0:16:36.84,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,So wait till tomorrow, 'kay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.46,0:16:40.78,Normal,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Really? You'll help me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.13,0:16:41.93,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.93,0:16:42.35,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,I will, {\alpha&FF&}I will, I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.35,0:16:42.55,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,I will, I will, {\alpha&FF&}I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.55,0:16:42.95,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,I will, I will, I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.95,0:16:43.60,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.08,0:16:47.45,Normal,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,You'll do anything... like a dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.01,0:16:50.04,Normal,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,You'll obediently do anything for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.49,0:16:51.06,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,I will. {\alpha&FF&}I swear!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.06,0:16:51.60,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,I will. I swear!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.35,0:16:55.19,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,So let's just drop this, alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.61,0:16:56.08,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.65,0:17:04.77,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how she got through the window?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.22,0:17:05.74,Normal,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Well—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.13,0:17:07.32,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'll take you back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.66,0:17:10.29,Normal,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,It's alright. I'm close anyway. Plus I have a wooden sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.59,0:17:11.73,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,No... That's what's dangerous...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.27,0:17:13.65,Normal,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, that hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.80,0:17:20.13,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... Well, I can get away by sticking a piece of paper if it's just that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.34,0:17:21.81,Normal,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,This note...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.24,0:17:24.43,Normal,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,You can use it if you'd like.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.63,0:17:28.15,Normal,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,If it's going to cost you money, I'll properly pay you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.00,0:17:31.00,Normal,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,See ya later, Ryuuji.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.25,0:17:32.49,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.38,0:17:37.88,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,Did she just call me by my first name?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.40,0:17:57.07,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, this is the Taka—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.07,0:17:59.16,Normal,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,HURRY AND GET OVER HERE! YOU'RE—!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.23,0:18:06.54,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.54,0:18:07.46,Normal,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,You just hung up, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.56,0:18:11.35,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,Where is it that you want me to hurry to anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.68,0:18:13.05,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.65,0:18:18.50,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,Veranda... Why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.34,0:18:22.03,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.49,0:18:25.13,Normal,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you say that you'd do anything, just like a dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.29,0:18:29.60,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a second! What I meant yesterday was that I'd help you with the Kitamura issu—!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.60,0:18:31.73,Normal,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,You know what's going to happen if you don't get over here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.12,0:18:34.22,Normal,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Or if you want I can help you understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.22,0:18:38.38,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,Well... Could you wait just 10 minutes?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.77,0:18:41.07,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,The rice is going to finish cooking around 10 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.08,0:18:42.60,Normal,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Three?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.02,0:18:52.07,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,You want some too?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.20,0:19:12.51,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.82,0:19:20.05,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,E-Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.11,0:19:21.53,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.15,0:19:24.22,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,It's open?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.43,0:19:28.96,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,What is that SMELL?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.17,0:19:33.15,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,Aisaka-san, I'm coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.22,0:19:35.91,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,That's a horrible smell.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.00,0:19:45.14,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,AISAKA!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.10,0:19:48.98,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,Aisaka! {\alpha&FF&}Aisaka! Aisaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.98,0:19:49.84,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,Aisaka! Aisaka! {\alpha&FF&}Aisaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.84,0:19:50.35,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,Aisaka! Aisaka! Aisaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.30,0:19:52.17,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,Please! {\alpha&FF&}Please let me—!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.17,0:19:53.31,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,Please! Please let me—!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.99,0:19:56.90,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,CLEAN THE KITCHEN IN THIS HOUSE!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.04,0:20:02.97,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,What this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.35,0:20:05.31,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,She went back to sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.43,0:20:10.96,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,She's like something that was man-made.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.80,0:20:15.93,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The sleeping Aisaka was really like a doll and—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.88,0:20:21.17,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She made this lifeless house look like a toy house set.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.64,0:20:26.40,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But it's too big for a doll's house.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.80,0:20:32.58,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,I'd say about 15 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.47,0:20:35.09,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.01,0:20:55.65,Normal,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.85,0:21:01.15,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.61,0:21:05.53,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still in the middle of it, but its pretty clean now isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.27,0:21:07.63,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,It was horrendous!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.63,0:21:09.44,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,The water that accumulated in the sink had begun rotting.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.54,0:21:13.12,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,And the drain was filled with sludge, mold and rotten food, a picture of hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.66,0:21:15.77,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,The rooms were so dusty—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.31,0:21:19.11,Normal,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Trespassing... and cleaning without permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.65,0:21:21.78,Normal,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't leave your markings everywhere, did you, you dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.97,0:21:22.74,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,Dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.89,0:21:24.95,Normal,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Oh wait, that would be an insult to dogs.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.20,0:21:27.31,Normal,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Even though you're a dog, you're a mutt.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.52,0:21:27.86,Normal,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,M-
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.86,0:21:28.22,Normal,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,M-U-
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.22,0:21:28.42,Normal,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,M-U-TT.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.88,0:21:32.62,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,This woman has no sense of gratitude. I just went through all this—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.56,0:21:43.17,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, aren't you going to say grace?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.27,0:21:49.61,Normal,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,God of rice and everyone that produced it, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.09,0:21:52.13,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.56,0:21:56.36,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, your nose stopped running.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.52,0:22:00.06,Normal,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's probably because this rooms all clean...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.54,0:22:01.96,Normal,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? What did you just say?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.96,0:22:02.90,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.53,0:23:36.61,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,A tedious pact.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.61,0:23:37.52,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,The misconceptions that begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.52,0:23:39.03,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,The power of genes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.03,0:23:42.41,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga, you're such a klutz that it's almost admirable.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.41,0:23:44.20,Normal,Ryuu,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up... and rot!
